<TEXTAREA NAME="ReplyMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">[QUOTE]Originally posted by Bugbok:
[B]I too have noticed that my slam does not refresh fast enough to interrupt some of the casters (e.g. Greater Ice Bones)  Instead of relying on the Mob's casting emotes, I usually slam as soon as I see "X begins to cast a spell"

Often times when I am soloing (e.g. pyramid in Cazic) where there are casters that can also heal, I will save my last few slams to interupt their heals instead of wasting them on the nukes.  I personally would rather get nuked and hope that I resist it then have the Mob heal back 2/3 of its life.[/B][/QUOTE]

</TEXTAREA>
